race.comment: TUSKEN WARRIOR (4) scored (21.78) last time out at this track adding to an already respectable career. Is yet to taste defeat at this course. In top form and looks a key chance again. MY BOY TWIST (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 4 lengths (17.13) at Q Straight. Expected to give a good account. LAMIA LUCCA (3) missed the frame last time when fourth (23.66) at Casino but prior to that had two placings in a row. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can measure up this time. ASAWA BABY (7) looks an each-way chance.
